NK010(tha)013:0: dpal chen rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs kyi bdag 'jug byin rlabs rol mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK010(tha)013:1: na mahsh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra ya /
NK010(tha)013:2: dpal chen rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug par 'dod pas /
NK010(tha)013:3: rang gi chos nyid bde gshegs snying po dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor rdzogs pa la /
NK010(tha)013:4: glo bur ba'i tshogs brgyad 'dus byas pa slob ma'i
NK010(tha)013:5: tshul du byas nas dbang gi bya ba la 'jug
NK010(tha)013:6: pa'i tshul nges par byas nas khrus byas /
NK010(tha)013:8: me tog bkye bsdu byas la /
NK010(tha)013:10: tsak+shur+b+han+d+ha wa ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)013:12: +aa kham b+ai ra h+aum gis me tog bzung la /
NK010(tha)013:14: khrag 'thung rdo rje he ru ka /
NK010(tha)013:15: bdag gis bdud rtsi lngas mchod de //
NK010(tha)013:16: bdag ni rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK010(tha)013:17: mi phyed rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)013:20: skal ldan rig 'dzin rigs kyi bu //
NK010(tha)013:21: lhag pa'i bsam pa bzang po'i phyir //
NK010(tha)013:22: da lta'i dus ni sems bskyed na //
NK010(tha)013:23: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK010(tha)013:24: zhes pa'i lan du slob bus /
NK010(tha)013:25: bdag ni skal bzang bde chen la //
NK010(tha)013:26: bde chen mchog la bdag dga' ste //
NK010(tha)013:27: bla med byang chub 'thob bya'i phyir //
NK010(tha)013:29: sdom pa thun mong bsgrag pa ni /
NK010(tha)013:32: rigs kyi bu khyod 'jug par byos //
NK010(tha)013:33: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa yi //
NK010(tha)013:34: dam tshig gnyan la khyod ma 'da' //
NK010(tha)013:35: dkyil 'khor gsang ba ma mthong zhing //
NK010(tha)013:36: gsang ba dam pa ma mthong la //
NK010(tha)013:37: gsang ba dam pa smra ma byed //
NK010(tha)013:38: khyod kyis sems can srog ma gcod //
NK010(tha)013:39: ma byin len dang rdzun la sogs //
NK010(tha)013:40: mi dge'i las rnams spang bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:41: de nas smon 'jug stabs gcig tu gzung ba'i phyir /
NK010(tha)013:43: skye rga na dang 'chi ba yi //
NK010(tha)013:44: chu srin pir thogs 'jigs byed las //
NK010(tha)013:45: gdon par nus pa khyod 'ba' zhig /
NK010(tha)013:46: dga' chen khyod bdag ston par bas //
NK010(tha)013:47: mgon po chen po bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)013:48: byang chub chen po'i tshul ston pa //
NK010(tha)013:49: dam tshig de nyid bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)013:50: byang chub sems kyang bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)013:51: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK010(tha)013:52: skyabs gsum dag kyang bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)013:53: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK010(tha)013:54: mgon po chen pos gzung du gsol //
NK010(tha)013:56: de nas sdom pa'i gzhi rten skyabs 'gro ni /
NK010(tha)013:57: chos sku mkha' 'dra gzugs sku 'ja' ltar snang //
NK010(tha)013:58: gsang sngags sgra snyan lta bur sgra bsgrags shing //
NK010(tha)013:59: khro bo khro mo'i tshul gyis gdug pa 'dul //
NK010(tha)013:60: bla med dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK010(tha)013:61: lan gsum gyi mthar smon 'jug gi sdom pa bzung ba dngos ni mos pa brtan pos /
NK010(tha)013:62: bdag gi byang chub sems mchog ni //
NK010(tha)013:63: ma lus par ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:64: ngan song gsum las ma grol ba //
NK010(tha)013:65: lha mi gnyis su dgrol bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:66: ma bsgral ba yi lha mi rnams //
NK010(tha)013:67: byang chub sa la bsgral bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:68: dbugs ma phyung ba'i byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)013:69: sa brgyad pa la dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK010(tha)013:70: sems can mya ngan 'das pa'i mtha' //
NK010(tha)013:71: rdo rjee 'chang la rab tu dgod //
NK010(tha)013:73: de nas rdo rje'i rnal 'byor du sems bskyed pa'i phyir gsol ba gdab ni /
NK010(tha)013:74: rdo rje ye shes chen po yi //
NK010(tha)013:75: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)013:76: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ste //
NK010(tha)013:77: de ring bdag la dbang bskur shog /
NK010(tha)013:78: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)013:79: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK010(tha)013:80: ma lus gzhung bzhin bsgrubs nas ni //
NK010(tha)013:81: sku gsung thugs kyi phur pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)013:82: ye shes rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)013:83: bdag gi dad pas 'jug par bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:84: rdo rje 'joms byed chen po yis //
NK010(tha)013:85: bdag la dbang mchog de ring gsol //
NK010(tha)013:88: nga ni ye shes rdo rje ste //
NK010(tha)013:89: nyon mongs rnam rtog 'joms pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)013:91: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK010(tha)013:92: zhes brjod nas slob bu'i snying gar bzhag la /
NK010(tha)013:93: khyed gzhan don du sangs rgyas sgrub par 'dun pa'i
NK010(tha)013:94: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems de nyid snying gar
NK010(tha)013:95: zla ba nya gang ba'i steng du don dam pa'i
NK010(tha)013:96: byang chub kyi sems rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'od
NK010(tha)013:97: zer lnga ldan gyi rnam pa can du sgoms la
NK010(tha)013:98: thams cad rnal 'byor du sems bskyed pa 'di'i rjes
NK010(tha)013:100: sarba yo ga tsit+ta ut+pa ta y+aa mi /
NK010(tha)013:103: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK010(tha)013:104: rnam rtog 'joms phyir ye shes gsal //
NK010(tha)013:105: sangs rgyas bdag la dbang ldan shog /
NK010(tha)013:107: sngags sdom bye brag pa bzung ba ni /
NK010(tha)013:109: sangs rgyas kun gyis grub pa'i gzhi //
NK010(tha)013:110: bla med rdo rje dam tshig ste //
NK010(tha)013:111: dam tshig 'di ni gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:112: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK010(tha)013:113: dkon mchog mkha' 'gro yang dag gzung //
NK010(tha)013:114: phyag rgya sngags rnams rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)013:115: yang dag lam la zhugs la byams //
NK010(tha)013:116: gsang ba chen po smra mi bya //
NK010(tha)013:117: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams gzung //
NK010(tha)013:118: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK010(tha)013:119: zhe sdang gti mug chags nga rgyal //
NK010(tha)013:120: dkar dmar ljang ser mthing ga'i mdog /
NK010(tha)013:121: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK010(tha)013:122: yan lag bcu yi dam tshig mdo //
NK010(tha)013:123: bdag gis brtan por gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)013:124: nam du yang ni mi spang ngo //
NK010(tha)013:125: lan gsum gyis sngags sdom thob par nges shes bskyed do //
NK010(tha)013:128: de ring khyod kyi snying la ni //
NK010(tha)013:129: rdo rje sems dpa' yang dag gnas //
NK010(tha)013:130: gal te tshul 'di dral gyur na //
NK010(tha)013:131: skad cig gis ni dral te gshegs //
NK010(tha)013:132: de bas dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK010(tha)013:134: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK010(tha)013:135: phyag na rdo rje nga yin gyi //
NK010(tha)013:136: nga yis smras pa thams cad kyang //
NK010(tha)013:137: nges pa kho nar bya dgos so //
NK010(tha)013:138: bdag la smad par ma byed cig /
NK010(tha)013:139: gal te smad par byas na ni //
NK010(tha)013:140: tshe yi 'du byed byas nas kyang //
NK010(tha)013:141: dam chu 'di yis rkyen byas nas //
NK010(tha)013:142: rdo rje'i dmyal bar gyur ta re //
NK010(tha)013:143: skal dang ldan pa rigs kyi bu //
NK010(tha)013:144: khyod kyis bsrung bar bya ba ni //
NK010(tha)013:145: lha dang bla ma spun mi spang //
NK010(tha)013:146: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)013:147: gsang ba gzhan la spel mi bya //
NK010(tha)013:148: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ste //
NK010(tha)013:149: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nges thub na //
NK010(tha)013:150: dam chu 'di yis rkyen byas nas //
NK010(tha)013:151: ye shes sems dpa' nyid du 'gyur //
NK010(tha)013:152: de nas phyi ltar 'jug pa dngos ni /
NK010(tha)013:154: zhes brjod pas phye tshul lho sgo snying rje chen
NK010(tha)013:155: po nas rim par phye yang 'jug tshul shar sgo
NK010(tha)013:156: nas g.yas skor du zhugs par bsams la /
NK010(tha)013:162: zhes sgo so sor sku gsung thugs phyag re bya /
NK010(tha)013:163: nang 'jug gi don du gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)013:165: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)013:166: ngang nyid rdo rje chos nyid las //
NK010(tha)013:167: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK010(tha)013:168: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)013:169: ces brjod pas dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yab yum bde ba chen po'i rba rlabs g.yos /
NK010(tha)013:170: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+nana bam h+aum h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:171: ces brjod pa'i sgra dang 'od zer gyis slob ma'i rnam smin gyi phung po sbyang /
NK010(tha)013:172: rnam par shes pa la ngo bo nyid med pa ni chos kyi sku /
NK010(tha)013:173: de'i ngang las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin h+aum du gyur pa yab kyi zhal nas drang /
NK010(tha)013:174: yum gyi b+ha gar rdo rje gzhon nur smin pas sku gsum rdzogs /
NK010(tha)013:175: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes brjod pas phyir phyung
NK010(tha)013:176: ste yab kyi phyag rigs lnga yab yum du gyur
NK010(tha)013:177: pas blang / sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)013:178: zhes brjod pas bde ba'i rlabs kyis dbang bzhi bskur /
NK010(tha)013:179: de la ye shes dbab pa'i phyir spos rol bya
NK010(tha)013:180: zhing rdzas kyi sbyor ba dmigs bsal bsreg pa dang
NK010(tha)013:182: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)013:183: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)013:184: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)013:185: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag gsol cig /
NK010(tha)013:186: sangs rgyas 'dus pa thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)013:187: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)013:188: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya a be sha ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:190: phebs rtags byung ma thag spyi bor rdo rje rgya gram du 'jog cing /
NK010(tha)013:191: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma gu la pra ta h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:192: ces brjod pas brtan par bya /
NK010(tha)013:193: de nas rigs dang las 'brel brtag pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor dngos sam /
NK010(tha)013:194: re kh+aa'i nang du me tog sngon po sna tshogs phyi rol du ma 'das par dor zhing /
NK010(tha)013:197: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)013:198: rdo rje rigs kyi me tog dor nas kyang //
NK010(tha)013:199: khrag 'thung rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs kyi //
NK010(tha)013:200: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rab 'byams rnams //
NK010(tha)013:201: skal ldan rig 'dzin bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)013:202: bdag ni rdo rje'i rigs su gzung du gsol //
NK010(tha)013:203: bo d+hi tsit+ta p+au tsa hoh de nas bla mas
NK010(tha)013:204: rigs de dang mthun pa'i ming gdags shing dngos grub
NK010(tha)013:206: lhag pa'i lha des rjes su 'dzin pa'i rten 'brel
NK010(tha)013:207: sgrig phyir slar yang cod pan spyi bor bcing zhing
NK010(tha)013:208: / de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK010(tha)013:209: ming ni rdo rje che ge mo //
NK010(tha)013:211: rdo rje kun grags yin par nges //
NK010(tha)013:212: rdo rje'i mtshan gyis kun grags shog /
NK010(tha)013:213: de nas mig dbye ba ni /
NK010(tha)013:215: sngon tshe mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK010(tha)013:216: gser gyi gtsags bu thogs nas ni //
NK010(tha)013:217: mig gi ling thog bsal ba ltar //
NK010(tha)013:218: thugs rje ye shes thabs ldan pas //
NK010(tha)013:219: mi shes rmongs pa'i rab rib dang //
NK010(tha)013:220: ma rig mug pa bsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)013:221: deng khyod rdo rje sems kyis ni //
NK010(tha)013:222: mig kun nges par 'byed mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)013:223: mig 'byed pa la brtson par byed //
NK010(tha)013:224: rdo rje'i mig tu bla med 'gyur //
NK010(tha)013:225: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsak+shu pra we sha phata /
NK010(tha)013:228: chos rnams gzugs brnyan 'dra ba yi //
NK010(tha)013:229: rang bzhin dag par rnyog pa med //
NK010(tha)013:230: gzugs brnyan gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)013:231: kun gyis dri ma med mthong shog /
NK010(tha)013:232: dkyil 'khor nyid la da lta nyid //
NK010(tha)013:233: dad pa'i shugs kyis blta bar gyis //
NK010(tha)013:234: khyod kyang sangs rgyas rigs las skyes //
NK010(tha)013:235: sngags dang phyag rgya'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)013:237: badz+ra man+dala pra we sha ho /
NK010(tha)013:238: e ma snod dang ldan pa'i bu //
NK010(tha)013:240: tshon rtsi mthong bas sdig las grol //
NK010(tha)013:241: de phyir dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK010(tha)013:242: rtags kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ni //
NK010(tha)013:243: don gyi 'og min nyid yin te //
NK010(tha)013:244: byang chub phyogs kyi chos kun dang //
NK010(tha)013:245: sa lam 'bras bu'i yon tan rdzogs //
NK010(tha)013:246: de na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kun //
NK010(tha)013:247: rang gi sems su shes par gyis //
NK010(tha)013:248: sems ni chos nyid la gnas pas //
NK010(tha)013:249: rang byung lhun grub dkyil 'khor yin //
NK010(tha)013:251: de nas dbang dngos gzhi'i slad du gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)013:252: thams cad mkhyen pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)013:253: rigs lnga 'dus pa'i khro rgyal gtso //
NK010(tha)013:254: rdo rje gzhon nu khros pa'i dpal //
NK010(tha)013:255: skal ldan rnams kyis thob par shog /
NK010(tha)013:257: de nas rig pa'i dbang lnga ni /
NK010(tha)013:258: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa
NK010(tha)013:259: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rnam par
NK010(tha)013:261: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis bdag la mngon par dbang bskur du gsol /
NK010(tha)013:264: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis dbang gi dgongs pa mdzad /
NK010(tha)013:265: gshegs ma rnams kyis bum pa yo bar bzung nas dbang bskur /
NK010(tha)013:266: sems dpa' rnams kyis shis pa brjod /
NK010(tha)013:267: sems ma rnams kyis glu gar bsgyur /
NK010(tha)013:268: khro bo rnams kyis bgegs bskrad de rig dbang lnga'i
NK010(tha)013:269: bya ba mdzad pa'i dag bya dag 'bras la bde
NK010(tha)013:270: stong gnyis su med pa'i nyams skyes par gyur /
NK010(tha)013:271: rnam bum spyi bor bzhag la /
NK010(tha)013:273: gsang gsum dam tshig las byung ba //
NK010(tha)013:274: yab yum gnyis med bde chen las //
NK010(tha)013:275: byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun 'dis //
NK010(tha)013:276: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)013:277: bo d+hi tsit+ta +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:278: rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i
NK010(tha)013:279: ngo bo bum pa'i chus dbang bskur zhing nye reg
NK010(tha)013:280: byas pas lus kyi sgrib pa dag /
NK010(tha)013:281: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i dbang thob /
NK010(tha)013:282: gzugs kyi phung po rdo rje mi bskyod pa dang /
NK010(tha)013:283: chu'i khams m+aa ma k+ai'i rang bzhin du gnas 'gyur /
NK010(tha)013:284: zhe sdang me long lta bu'i ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)013:285: sangs rgyas rdo rje rigs kyi sku rnam pa thams
NK010(tha)013:286: cad kyi bdag nyid 'gyur ba med pa thob nas
NK010(tha)013:289: de nas rin 'byung dbu rgyan gyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:290: dbang 'di thob nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rgyal
NK010(tha)013:291: thabs la dbang bas na rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan la
NK010(tha)013:292: thob pa lnga'i sgra chags pa ste /
NK010(tha)013:293: de nyid mgo la bkon nas /
NK010(tha)013:295: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal srid che //
NK010(tha)013:296: thob pa lnga yi dbang bskur ba //
NK010(tha)013:297: rin chen rigs kyi dbang bskur mchog /
NK010(tha)013:298: rin chen khrag 'thung brtan gyur cig /
NK010(tha)013:299: sa ma ta rat+na badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:300: rigs kyi bu khyod la dbu rgyan 'di bkon pa
NK010(tha)013:301: tsam gyis sgo gsum gyi rmongs pa'i sgrib pa dag
NK010(tha)013:302: / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yon tan gyi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)013:303: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK010(tha)013:304: sa'i khams sangs rgyas spyan mar gnas 'gyur /
NK010(tha)013:305: nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)013:306: sangs rgyas rin chen rigs kyi yon tan thams cad mkhyen nas 'gro ba'i don byed par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)013:307: snang mtha' rdo rje'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:308: +aah sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK010(tha)013:309: rdo rje gsung gi don mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)013:311: rdo rje chos kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)013:312: pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:313: rigs kyi bu khyod la snang ba mtha' yas kyi
NK010(tha)013:314: rang bzhin rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas ngag gi sgrib
NK010(tha)013:315: pa dag / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung gi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)013:316: 'du shes kyi phung po snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK010(tha)013:317: me'i khams gos dkar mor gnas 'gyur /
NK010(tha)013:318: 'dod chags so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)013:319: sangs rgyas pad+ma rigs kyi gsung 'gag pa med pa'i
NK010(tha)013:320: chos kyi sgra dbyangs thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed
NK010(tha)013:321: par 'gyur ro // don yod grub pa dril bu'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:323: mkha' 'gro kun gyi dril bu'i dbang //
NK010(tha)013:324: rtog med chos kyi sgra 'byin cing //
NK010(tha)013:325: las kyi khrag 'thung phrin las bdag /
NK010(tha)013:326: shes rab dril bu'i dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)013:327: krit+ta a nush+tha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:328: rigs kyi bu khyod la dril bu 'di gtad pa
NK010(tha)013:329: tsam gyis nyon mongs pa bag la nyal gyi sgrib
NK010(tha)013:330: pa dag / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phrin las kyi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)013:331: 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub pa dang /
NK010(tha)013:332: rlung gi khams dam tshig sgrol mar gnas 'gyur /
NK010(tha)013:333: phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)013:335: rnam par snang mdzad ming gi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:337: sngar gyi gsang ming dkyil 'khor pa'i lha tshogs kyis 'ur dir bsgrags par bsam nas //
NK010(tha)013:338: rdo rje ming gi chos nyid de //
NK010(tha)013:339: cis kyang mi tshugs mi shigs te //
NK010(tha)013:340: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)013:341: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)013:342: d+harma d+h+aa tu bi sho d+ha badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:343: rigs kyi bu khyod la rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK010(tha)013:344: ngo bo ming che ge mo btags pa tsam gyis
NK010(tha)013:346: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs kyi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)013:347: rnam par shes pa'i phung po rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK010(tha)013:348: nam mkha'i khams chos kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug mar gnas gyur /
NK010(tha)013:349: gti mug chos dbyings ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)013:350: sangs rgyas de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rnam par mi
NK010(tha)013:351: rtog pa thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed par 'gyur
NK010(tha)013:352: ro // de ltar rig dbang lnga thob pa'i bral thob ni /
NK010(tha)013:354: sangs rgyas lngar ni rnam dag pa'i //
NK010(tha)013:355: dbang bskur lnga thob rgyud la ni //
NK010(tha)013:356: ma rig pa dang bral bas na //
NK010(tha)013:357: ye shes lnga ni thob par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)013:359: de nas rig dbang lnga'i mtha' rten du snang zhen
NK010(tha)013:360: lha skur rdzogs byed rnam rgyal bum pa'i dbang ni
NK010(tha)013:361: / bum pa spyi bor bzung la /
NK010(tha)013:363: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK010(tha)013:365: g.yon nas yum gyis yab la 'khyud //
NK010(tha)013:366: phyag gi bum pa rab tu blangs //
NK010(tha)013:367: ye shes dbang gi chu bo 'di //
NK010(tha)013:368: nyon mongs ma gos dkar la 'tsher //
NK010(tha)013:369: skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyod la //
NK010(tha)013:370: spyi bor bum pas dbang bskur bas //
NK010(tha)013:371: nyon mongs gsum dang dug gsum sbyangs //
NK010(tha)013:372: dbang gi chu bo rgyun bzhin 'bab //
NK010(tha)013:373: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:374: d+aip+ta tsakra ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK010(tha)013:376: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:377: gtso bo'i sku spyi bor bskur la /
NK010(tha)013:379: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NK010(tha)013:380: thugs rjes khams gsum gdug pa 'dul //
NK010(tha)013:381: gnyen pos las su rung mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)013:382: 'jigs byed gnyen po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)013:383: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:384: k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:385: dar le brgan la sngags byang bris pa mgrin pa bzung la /
NK010(tha)013:387: gsung gi rang bzhin mtshon byed pa'i //
NK010(tha)013:388: le brgan 'bar ba'i kha dog la //
NK010(tha)013:389: snying po nus pa'i don dang ldan //
NK010(tha)013:390: nus pa can gyi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)013:391: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:392: w+aa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:393: phur pa snying gar bzhag la /
NK010(tha)013:395: tsit+ta smug po'i gzhal yas nas //
NK010(tha)013:396: khams gsum dbang gi bdag po ste //
NK010(tha)013:397: brkyang bskum rab tu gdengs pa yis //
NK010(tha)013:398: gdug pa 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)013:399: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:401: yon tan dang phrin las gnyis ka'i dbang ye shes sems dpa'i tsakli snying gar gtad la /
NK010(tha)013:403: thugs ka rin cen zur brgyad las //
NK010(tha)013:404: phrin las sna tshogs lhun gyis grub //
NK010(tha)013:405: thams cad kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK010(tha)013:406: ye shes sems dpa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)013:407: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)013:408: gu na karma a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)013:409: de nas dur khrod chas brgyad kyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:411: zhing chen g.yang gzhis 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod //
NK010(tha)013:412: glang chen ko rlon thugs rje stobs kyi bdag /
NK010(tha)013:413: stag sham yon tan phrin las rgyas pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)013:414: bdud chas dpa' bo'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)013:416: thod pa rlon pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)013:417: thod pa skam po chos kyi sku yi rtags //
NK010(tha)013:418: thod pa tshal bu sprul pa sku yi rtags //
NK010(tha)013:419: sku gsum mtshon byed thod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)013:421: rigs bzhi klu rnams ma lus 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK010(tha)013:422: gdug pa sbrul ni rigs bzhis sku la brgyan //
NK010(tha)013:423: zhe sdang chen po gnas su 'joms mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)013:424: gdug pa chas kyi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)013:426: zhag gi zo ris dam rdzas bcud kyi rgyan //
NK010(tha)013:427: thal chen tshom bu 'khor ba 'joms pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)013:428: rak+ta'i thig le thugs rje chags pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)013:429: mtshan ma rnam pa gsum gyi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)013:430: de la dag pa brjod pa ni /
NK010(tha)013:431: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang ni //
NK010(tha)013:432: yon tan phrin las lnga ru bskur //
NK010(tha)013:433: phyogs bcu srog la dbang bskur bas //
NK010(tha)013:434: srog ni ye shes gyur nas ni //
NK010(tha)013:435: khams gsum sgrol ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)013:436: zhes brjod pas phur pa'i sgos chos dkyil 'khor gsum gyi srog ye shes su dbang bskur ba dang /
NK010(tha)013:437: de las khams gsum gyi srog la dbang bskur ba'i don dbang mchog bzhin du dran par bya'o //
NK010(tha)013:438: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)013:441: thabs kyi spyod pas gzhan don du //
NK010(tha)013:442: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)013:443: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)013:444: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsal to //
NK010(tha)013:445: bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK010(tha)013:446: rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje dang dril bu
NK010(tha)013:447: 'di gtad cing dam tshig gsum byin nas rdo rje
NK010(tha)013:448: slob dpon du dbang bskur bas /
NK010(tha)013:449: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag nyid pha rol
NK010(tha)013:450: tu phyin pa drug gi rang bzhin sngags kyi lta
NK010(tha)013:451: spyod zab mo'i thabs shes zung 'brel du rdzogs nas
NK010(tha)013:452: / 'khor ba ma spangs rang bzhin med par dag /
NK010(tha)013:453: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pas 'gro ba'i don dpag
NK010(tha)013:454: tu med pa byed pa'i rten 'brel 'grig pa yin
NK010(tha)013:456: de ltar bum pa'i dbang bskur bas bskyed rim sgom pa'i snod du gyur /
NK010(tha)013:458: lus rags pa bzhin lag gi rnam pa tha mal du 'dzin pa dang /
NK010(tha)013:459: phra ba rtsa'i rnam grangs tha dad pa sbyangs pas sku rdo rje'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)013:460: lam bskyed pa'i rim pa dang dga' ba'i ye shes
NK010(tha)013:461: la brten nas bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa
NK010(tha)013:462: non / sprul pa'i sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud la bzhag pa yin no //
NK010(tha)013:464: dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yab yum snyoms par zhugs
NK010(tha)013:465: par mos pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin bde
NK010(tha)013:466: skyong gi snod du bskyil ba bdud rtsi lnga dang
NK010(tha)013:467: sbyar ba lce thog tu byin la /
NK010(tha)013:469: bde chen thig le yab yum bcu //
NK010(tha)013:471: bu yi lce la dbab par bya //
NK010(tha)013:472: snying gi dkyil du bzung bar gyis //
NK010(tha)013:473: bo d+hi tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa +aa /
NK010(tha)013:474: slob mas dang du blangs nas /
NK010(tha)013:477: +aahh+aum ma h+aa su kha hoh zhes brjod /
NK010(tha)013:478: de ltar gsang dbang bskur bas sgron ma lnga dang
NK010(tha)013:479: bdud rtsi lnga brten zhing lam tsan+da li dang bzlas
NK010(tha)013:482: dag bya ngag gi rang bzhin phra ba'i rlung la
NK010(tha)013:483: zhu bde las skyes pa'i byang chub kyi sems kun
NK010(tha)013:484: rdzob pa 'dres pas phra ba rlung dag rags pa
NK010(tha)013:486: gsung rdo rje'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)013:487: mchog dag'i ye shes la brten nas ma chags pad+ma can gyi sa non /
NK010(tha)013:488: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud la bzhag pa yin no //
NK010(tha)013:489: dbang gsum pa'i don du rig tsaka byin nas rtogs pa bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)013:491: bde ba thugs kyi sems dpa' che //
NK010(tha)013:492: yab yum gnyis med mu tig gi //
NK010(tha)013:493: khu 'phang byang sems phab pa yis //
NK010(tha)013:494: dus gsum bla ma sangs rgyas dang //
NK010(tha)013:495: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bde chen gyi //
NK010(tha)013:496: byang chub sems kyi mchod pa phul //
NK010(tha)013:497: rdo rje bde chen thig le'i dbyings //
NK010(tha)013:498: zag med dbyings su mi rtog skye //
NK010(tha)013:499: de bas blo mchog longs spyod cig /
NK010(tha)013:500: ces sbyin pa na rig mas /
NK010(tha)013:502: yab chen chos kyi dbyings mthong ba'i //
NK010(tha)013:504: de las byang chub sems 'khyil ba'i //
NK010(tha)013:505: zag med bde ba longs spyod dam //
NK010(tha)013:509: shes rab lha mo yum chen mo //
NK010(tha)013:510: chos kyi dbyings la 'o byed do //
NK010(tha)013:511: byang chub sems mthong thig le la //
NK010(tha)013:512: rtag tu gus shing bde ba sbyor //
NK010(tha)013:514: de nas rig ma pang du byon nas gsum pa'i dbang gi rtogs pa 'di brjod par bsam la /
NK010(tha)013:515: gar dang ldan pa yang dag bskyod //
NK010(tha)013:516: bde chen sgyu ma'i brda mtshon te //
NK010(tha)013:517: gnyis shor gnyis mnyam dbus dag tu //
NK010(tha)013:518: dbyings kyi bde chen 'byung ba de //
NK010(tha)013:519: rang rig ye shes de la yod //
NK010(tha)013:521: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis mnyam par rol pa la /
NK010(tha)013:522: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)013:523: a nu r+aa ga hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK010(tha)013:524: zhes yab yum brda dang brda len mdzad pas rjes su chags pa'i nyams brtas par bsam zhing /
NK010(tha)013:530: thugs rdo rje mi rtog pa /
NK010(tha)013:531: snying po chos nyid blo 'das las byung ba'i dga' bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong bar bsam mo //
NK010(tha)013:533: de ltar dbang gsum pa bskur bas dngos sam yid kyi sna tshogs gzugs can sgom pa la dbang /
NK010(tha)013:535: dga' ba bzhi'i mas brtan gyi dpe'i ye shes la brten nas rags pa thig le'i sgrib pa dag /
NK010(tha)013:536: phra ba yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK010(tha)013:537: de nyid rnam pa bcu drug gi don mngon du
NK010(tha)013:538: byas nas chos kyi sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud
NK010(tha)013:541: gsum pa'i lhan skyes kyi dpes bzhi pa'i ye shes
NK010(tha)013:542: mngon sum du mthong ba'i don la mnyam par bzhag
NK010(tha)013:543: la / ngo bo nyid kyi stong pa las //
NK010(tha)013:544: bdag dang chos dang rnam rig dang //
NK010(tha)013:545: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam spangs pa //
NK010(tha)013:546: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK010(tha)013:547: stong nyid ye nas gnas pa la //
NK010(tha)013:548: shes pas mthong ba'i yul min te //
NK010(tha)013:549: gang gis ye shes bskyed gyur pa //
NK010(tha)013:550: de yis ye shes rnam dag mthong //
NK010(tha)013:552: de ltar dbang bzhi pa bskur bas rnam rtog /
NK010(tha)013:553: 'joms byed chos nyid byang chub sems kyi phur pa sgom pa la dbang /
NK010(tha)013:555: kun gzhi lung ma bstan dang shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK010(tha)013:556: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs dang /
NK010(tha)013:557: slob ma'i sgo gsum rdul dang bral ba'i dwangs ma gsum ldan gcig tu 'dres /
NK010(tha)013:558: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la brten nas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa non /
NK010(tha)013:559: ngo bo nyid sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud la bzhag pa yin no //
NK010(tha)013:561: bum pa'i dam tshig gang yin la //
NK010(tha)013:562: bskyed pa'i rim pa brtag pa dang //
NK010(tha)013:563: rmongs pa rnams la mi bya ste //
NK010(tha)013:564: snod kyi lo ka gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)013:565: bcud kyi 'jig rten lha yi mchog /
NK010(tha)013:566: de ni bum pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK010(tha)013:567: gang zhig gsang ba ston pa la //
NK010(tha)013:568: gsang ba'i dam tshig 'di yin te //
NK010(tha)013:569: bud med shes rab rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)013:570: tsan+da li la rtag tu bsgom //
NK010(tha)013:571: zas lnga rtag tu bza' bar bya //
NK010(tha)013:572: spyad par bya ba'i mchog yin no //
NK010(tha)013:573: ye shes chen po'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)013:574: mo rnams kun la spyad pa dang //
NK010(tha)013:575: dga' ba rtag tu brten par bya //
NK010(tha)013:576: sems kyang d+h+au tir blta bar bya //
NK010(tha)013:577: ye shes snying po'i dam tshig go //
NK010(tha)013:579: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK010(tha)013:581: sku drin gtang rag gi yon du man+dala dbul /
NK010(tha)013:582: dge ba bsngo ba spyi ltar bya'o //
NK010(tha)013:583: de nyid rig pa'i rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK010(tha)013:584: sbyor ba 'dis kyang cho ga ma 'khrug par //
NK010(tha)013:585: smin par nus pa'i rten 'brel bsgrig nus pa //
NK010(tha)013:586: dbang po rnon pa'i snod kyi khyad par yin //
